                             CHANGES

                    Java(tm) Development Kit
                   JDK(tm) 1.1.8_009 Software
                            
This CHANGES file summarizes the changes between the FCS version of 
JDK/JRE 1.1.8 and this patch version, JDK/JRE 1.1.8_009. For changes
in the Java platform since earlier releases, see the 
following document on the Java Software web site:

       http://java.sun.com/products/jdk/1.1/changes.html
                           
                                                        
-----------------------------------------------------------------------                                                                                                                                                                                                      
INTRODUCTION
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
This is patch 009 of the 1.1.8 version of the Java Development
Kit. This is the Win32 production implementation and the Solaris
reference implementation from Java Software Division of Sun
Microsystems. For full details about using the Java Development Kit,
please read the original README that comes with the JDK1.1.8 Java
Development Kit.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
